text: Herkimer County is a county in the U.S. state of New York. As of the 2020 census, 60,139 people lived there. The county seat is Herkimer. Parts of this county is part of New York's 21st congressional district. ==References== Category:New York (state) counties Category:1791 establishments in New York (state)
